## 🔹 Overview
This project is a *Power BI dashboard* that analyzes *pizza sales data* using *SQL and Power BI. It provides insights into *revenue, top-selling pizzas, worst-selling pizzas, and order trends*.

## 📌 Key Features
✅ *Total Revenue & Orders*  
✅ *Top 5 & Bottom 5 Pizzas by Revenue, Quantity, and Orders*  
✅ *Best & Worst Selling Days & Times*  
✅ *Data-driven insights for better decision-making*  

## 🛠️ Tools Used
- *SQL* (Data extraction & transformation)  
- *Power BI* (Dashboard creation & visualization)  

## 📂 Project Files
- PIZZA SALES REPORT.pbix → Power BI file with interactive visualizations.  

